description:
Cultural and creative matrix, national key

However, it is difficult for the cultural industry to gain financial regurgitation-feeding

"Harry Potter", after being refused by the publishing house for seven times, finally swept around the world and got the value of 100 billion

For it bears the cultural emotion of a generation; the huge consensus brings huge values

It is a pity that fans gain few benefit

CRYSTO constructs the global cultural industry with token finance

All human beings cooperate to jointly construct and share the big circulation ecology of culture
name: CRYSTO
